OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777986670
OL,3,CPub-goer who killed man with punch
OL,4,Ctells court it was 'self-defence'
OL,6,FGothard, of Church Street, Appleby
OL,7,FMagna, sat with his head down in the
OL,8,Fdock while the jury listened to the
OL,9,Fclosing speeches.
OL,11,FHe denies murder and an alternative
OL,12,Fcharge of manslaughter.
OL,14,FJurors were told they will retire to
OL,15,Fbegin their deliberations on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
